# Secrets and rendered configs — NEVER commit
**/.local.env
**/.run/

# Bulky / raw Checkbox artifacts. The committed results are RESULT.md (human
# summary) + the junit.xml (per-test pass/fail). The raw submission bundle, full
# JSON, and HTML report are regenerable with `run-*.sh collect`, so they are not
# committed to keep the repo small. Un-ignore any of these if you want them.
**/reports/*.tar.xz
**/reports/*.html
**/reports/*.json
**/reports/*.submission.log
